sequenceDiagram
participant Client as 客户端
participant Gateway as 网关服务
participant User as 用户服务
participant DB as 用户数据库

    Client->>Gateway: POST /user/api/auth/login
    Gateway->>User: 转发登录请求
    User->>DB: 查询用户信息
    DB-->>User: 返回用户数据
    User->>User: 验证密码
    User->>User: 生成Token
    User-->>Gateway: 返回登录响应(token+用户信息)
    Gateway-->>Client: 返回登录结